      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "威镇山岗，豪杰英雄保魏王。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00019",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "五湖四海把名扬，方显男儿志量强。帐中领了魏王令，追赶弟兄回山岗。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00020",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "俺，王勇字伯党。奉了魏王将令，追赶弟兄回山。众兵丁！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
