      "event_id": "05004010_e00024",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦琼、徐勣、罗成、程咬金同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00025",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "那旁人马喧嚷，这便怎处？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00026",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "想是魏王追兵到来，你我弟兄挡他一阵。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00027",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王伯党、四上手同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00028",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "呀，原来众家兄弟，有礼了。大家下马相见。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00029",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼",
        "徐勣",
        "罗成",
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "好，大家下马相见。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00030",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "请问众家弟兄因何不辞而往？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00031",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼",
        "徐勣",
        "罗成",
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "那昏王无道，我等难以辅保，后会有期。请了！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00032",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "请问众家弟兄，有什么不平之事，对俺王勇说个明白，你们再去未迟。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00033",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "好，我们对你说知，贤弟听道。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00034",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "兄弟相逢在路旁，尊一声贤弟听端详：昏王他把旨来降，南牢不放小秦王。石垒坚阵命未丧，反道我暗地保唐王。金殿哪容我分讲，推出午门把我伤。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00035",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "王勇闻言怒气上，这是昏王理不当。不念忠臣把国掌，哪个忠良保朝廊。回头又对三哥讲，你今散去为哪桩？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00036",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00037",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "六弟不必泪悲伤，提起心头恨魏王。只为二哥把本上，那昏王赶我出朝廊。他道我与贼同一党，巧改本章罪难当。动不动他把死罪降，谁肯抄手等无常？我今回转历城往，让他一人自称王。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00038",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "先生不把经纶掌，谁推八卦定阴阳？回头我对八弟讲，你把原由说端详？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00039",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "手挽手儿尊兄长，小弟言来听心旁。只为二哥把本上，反要将我过刀伤。无奈带了众家将，回转幽州乐安康。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00040",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "叫声八弟不必忙，年少英雄各一方。回头我对咬金讲，你今缘何散瓦岗？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00041",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "上前尊声六兄长，小弟略略表几桩：曾记当初招兵将，老程三斧取瓦岗。我今皇帝让他做，如今逞势坐朝堂。大家不在心头上，因此上各自走他的娘！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00042",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来怒满腔，指着金殿骂魏王。且看深山把虎养，毛衣长足把人伤。自古国乱思良将，家贫方显孝儿郎。低下头来暗思想，回头尊声众豪强：李密虽然他无道，悔不该当初把他降。依我相劝回山往，大王降罪我承当，料也无妨。",
      "text_length": 102
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00043",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟不必多言讲，愚兄岂肯心不良！李密为君少大量，实实不愿保昏王。逃笼鹊鸟鱼出网，历城县还有我亲娘。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00044",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "要我转去休妄想，萤火焉能见太阳？李密本是草寇相，真命天子是唐王。今日山前别兄往，去到太原保秦王。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00045",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "船到江心补漏难，马到临崖难收缰。自古养儿来侍老，太平积谷保饥荒。在此拜别六兄长，小弟归家奉高堂。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00046",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "我也不愿奉高堂，我也不愿回故乡。我也不愿保唐主，我也不愿扶魏王。我今回转历城往，贩卖竹筢度时光。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00047",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "众位弟兄想一想，做一个忠良万古扬。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00048",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "万古扬来万古扬，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00049",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "哪个忠良有下场！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00050",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "任你说的天花样，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00051",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "提起魏王恼心肠！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00052",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "他众人说话都一样，好叫王勇无主张。二哥、三哥还乡往，咬金、罗成归故乡。单单剩下王伯党，一人怎比众人强？低下头来暗思想，回头尊声众豪强：各把前事想一想，莫做无义小儿郎。而今若还不思想，惹动干戈岂寻常？",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00053",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "要杀要战齐动手，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00054",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "你有藤牌老子有枪。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00055",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "山前摆下杀人场，弟兄们今朝来来来战一场。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00056",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "一见弟兄动刀枪，倒叫秦琼着了忙。要杀就把愚兄斩，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00057",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "你来看！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00058",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "你家中还有你的伯母娘。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00059",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "山前哭坏王伯党！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00060",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "二哥、三哥、八弟呀！我那众兄弟呀！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00061",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "点点珠泪洒胸膛。手挽手儿尊兄长，小弟言来听端详：结义三十九员将，赛过了桃园刘关张。到如今各把心来散，枉费金炉一炷香。你们一一都去了，撇下王勇好凄凉！",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00062",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "六弟要去一路往，倒不如大家去降唐。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05004010_e00063",
      "play_id": "05004010",
      "scene_id": "05004010_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯党"
      ],
      "text": "我本当与你们一路往，一臣岂扶二君王？山前拜别众兄长！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
